Tilbury when they create an account.

157
00:06:25,860 --> 00:06:27,210
One of the really cool things

158
00:06:27,210 --> 00:06:30,420
about Trading 212 is they
let you practice investing

159
00:06:30,420 --> 00:06:32,640
with fake money so you can get familiar

160
00:06:32,640 --> 00:06:36,240
with real data from the markets
without risking any money.

161
00:06:36,240 --> 00:06:39,000
So if you're a little
uncomfortable with investing,

162
00:06:39,000 --> 00:06:40,860
or just want to try some strategies

163
00:06:40,860 --> 00:06:43,110
before putting your own money on the line,

164
