If you live in the UK or Europe,

172
00:07:00,570 --> 00:07:03,480
it's worth trying out
Trading 212 because signing

173
00:07:03,480 --> 00:07:06,330
up is completely free and
there are no commissions.

174
00:07:06,330 --> 00:07:08,940
Of course, don't forget
to use the code Tilbury

175
00:07:08,940 --> 00:07:10,620
and you'll receive a free share worth

176
